Detect Thermos/Bukkit and disable incompatible plugins.

* Village getBlock fix by @charagarlnad in https://github.com/GTNewHorizons/Hodgepodge/pull/7
* Added ability to automatically wake up personal & passive anchors on owner login by @repo-alt in https://github.com/GTNewHorizons/Hodgepodge/pull/12

## What's Changed
HodgePodge 2.0

* Uses GTNHMixins 2.0
* Uses IEarlyMixin and ILateMixin, Reorganized mixins into early/ and late/
* Does away with JAR based mod matching and now uses the list of loaded core mod classes, and mod ids
* Reorganized project structure to hopefully be a little more intuitive and minimize accidental early class loading
* Removed redundant getBlock() fixes [which were no longer working due to new application order anyway]
* Remove the GT5u saw fix - will reintroduce into GT5u
* Includes pre-release buildscript updates
* Faster TileEntity removal for World.updateEntities

Adaption of https://github.com/MinecraftForge/MinecraftForge/commit/638a54b04ab896fd18bdc5da48269f5465e5b61c
* Fixes https://github.com/GTNewHorizons/GT-New-Horizons-Modpack/issues/9147 when fastcraft & Bukket are not loaded
* Merge ModMixins back into Hodgepodge

Also disable Spotless on LoadingConfig; it's a nightmare to read otherwise!


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/GTNewHorizons/Hodgepodge/compare/1.7.37...2.0.0

Change log:
0.7.6 Fixed the Arc Furnace input be a Plasma Arc Furnace

1.0.0

Adding now full GT 5 support for Minetweaker Version 3.10
Need to be tested
Documentation will follow

Deleting old Machines that not exists any more

CNC, Grinder, Sonictron

Fix and Improve a lot of Machine recipes
Mixer, Separator, Centrifuge, Blast Furnace, Canner, ChemicalBath, Cutting Saw

Fix Blastfurnace Input 2
Fix Electrolyzer Error log
Adding Oredict support for the Input slots of each machines.
fix Pyrolyse oven spelling

Added ore support
Thanks to  Techlone

Ore dict support by Techlone

Beta Version needs to be tested.

* Mixer fix by @Techlone in https://github.com/GTNewHorizons/Minetweaker-Gregtech-5-Addon/pull/11

1.6.2 Fix registration of machines from 1.5.0
Added method for the six slots assembler

Added a low gravity flag in the autoclave
Added a fluid output in the blast furnace
Added a secondary output in the chem reactor

Added a PrimitiveBlastFurnace support
